    <item>
      <title>美国希望从冻结的俄罗斯资产中“释放经济价值”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/us-looking-to-unlock-economic-value-from-frozen-russian-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部一位高级官员表示，美国正在探索使用在乌克兰入侵爆发时冻结的 3000 亿美元俄罗斯国有资产的方案，以帮助支付这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家的重建费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/us-looking-to-unlock-economic-value-from-frozen-russian-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 14:35:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国推出自战争开始以来对俄罗斯最大规模的制裁方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/us-unveils-biggest-sanctions-package-on-russia-since-war-began</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国公布了自两年前入侵乌克兰以来针对俄罗斯最大规模的单日制裁计划，针对超过 500 名个人和实体，此举旨在挤压该国经济，并就异见人士阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼 (Alexey Navalny) 之死发出信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/us-unveils-biggest-sanctions-package-on-russia-since-war-began</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
