    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯叛逃者在度假村被杀让西班牙措手不及</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/russian-defector-s-murder-in-alicante-catches-spain-off-guard</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙对一名俄罗斯逃兵在热门旅游胜地被杀一事表示担忧，但在政府等待法医报告时并未将矛头指向克里姆林宫的安全部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/russian-defector-s-murder-in-alicante-catches-spain-off-guard</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将于下周开始向波兰提供 1370 亿欧元的援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/eu-to-begin-freeing-up-137-billion-in-polish-aid-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟委员会主席乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩周五表示，布鲁塞尔将从下周开始解冻向波兰支付高达1370亿欧元（1480亿美元）的援助，并赞扬华沙在多年民粹主义统治后恢复法治的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/eu-to-begin-freeing-up-137-billion-in-polish-aid-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 11:13:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰终止俄罗斯液化天然气进口的努力因总协议而受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/total-s-deal-stands-in-dutch-way-to-end-russian-lng-imports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TotalEnergies SE 与一家俄罗斯供应商之间的长期液化天然气合同已成为荷兰政府承诺停止从俄罗斯进口燃料的一个令人不安的障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/total-s-deal-stands-in-dutch-way-to-end-russian-lng-imports</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 10:32:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利在喷气式战斗机交易后允许瑞典加入北约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/hungary-s-orban-to-agree-arms-deal-with-sweden-before-nato-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·欧尔班证实，在瑞典同意向布达佩斯出售“鹰狮”喷气式战斗机后，匈牙利将消除瑞典加入北约的最后障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/hungary-s-orban-to-agree-arms-deal-with-sweden-before-nato-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 07:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
